title: All Ball - Pt. 2 of 2: Former Gonzaga Star Dan Dickau on Building Program Foundation, 2021 Zags, NBA Experience
itunes:title: All Ball - Pt. 2 of 2: Former Gonzaga Star Dan Dickau on Building Program Foundation, 2021 Zags, NBA Experience
description:
In this episode, Doug is joined by former Gonzaga superstar and NBA player Dan Dickau for the second part of a two part interview to discuss his breaking onto the national scene at Gonzaga, building the foundation of what the program has become, his NBA experience across multiple teams, and how he's staying involved in the game.
